| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4595 — Recovery Inhibition (meow)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 36c0edfb-2f4d-54cd-9312-9d526b7f7fb0"
